Business Analyst (BA)
Responsibilities
Review and give recommendation on all current business model files to ensure its accuracy and completenessCreate new business analytical reports to be used by the managementHandle ad-hoc request and queries related to business activitiesReview all expenses claims to ensure the documentation integrity based on current policiesBe back up for several finance & accounting activities, such as invoicing and receipt records Requirements: Age maximum 30 years oldFamiliar with SAP program would be advantage2-3 years’ experience in a recognized public accounting firms (big 4 would be an advantage)Experience in ISO certification is a must.Can work independently General Requirements: S1 from Economic  (accounting/management) background, with minimum GPA 8 or 3.00 of 4.00Ability to identify problems, strong conceptual and analytical thinkingMature, resourceful, self-motivated and result-orientedAble to work under pressureGood command of English and computer literate is a mustWorking experience in diagnostics or healthcare industry would be an advantage Submit your detailed resume & recent photograph to:sysmex@sysmex.co.idPlease indicate the position code on your email subject
